{"tid":1941711,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（代post)岩岩去完龍門學堂修甲 我有野講","createTime":"2020-03-24T14:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T18:04:20.000Z","uid":254302,"like":83,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"2711a7cbdc19e4b04d9b13588b032edde8d9c214","tid":1941711,"uid":254302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T14:55:48.000Z","msg":"當時人因為冇連登account，所以幫佢post一post<br />\n<br />\n事緣2月中既時候，見到龍門冰室開左個龍門學堂做Gel甲。我個陣打算去支持下同路人，所以報左3月24日去做（姐係今日），已經諗住遲一個月去冇咁伏，有一個月時間比佢地練。<br />\n<br />\n2月中個陣我已經Send好款比佢地做，諗住比佢地準備下，圖為以下：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hFKY4uJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhFKY4uJ.jpg&h=d621e113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到今日我去整，因為我之前有整開甲，需要拆甲，我都預左時間比佢地慢慢搞。<br />\n但係問題開始黎，過左一個鐘，佢仲拆緊甲。。。<br />\n到剪甲個陣，又驚斷甲又驚我痛，慢撚到我就黎訓著教先拆完。<br />\n<br />\n之後剪甲，佢可以剪到我左右手唔同長度。。。<br />\n圖示<br />\n左手： <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iMkabaX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiMkabaX.png&h=205a155d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n右手：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1iqabbc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1iqabbc.png&h=40ca97e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要最後佢搞左3個鐘，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係！呀！單色整左3個鐘！！！<br />\n</span> <br />\n仲要我放棄左個暈染，覺得佢整唔黎（佢有試過但真係搞唔掂），同佢講要深藍色，佢比左呢隻藍我，我都唔知講咩好啦。。。 <br />\n仲要收我300蚊。。我平時做開220蚊嫁咋。。真係當掉左落海。。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8dVJwbQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8dVJwbQ.png&h=66cb2c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於呢間野我都冇咩野好講，只係希望大家唔好好似我咁中伏。。。<br />\n我諗就算你幾黃，你打開門做生意都唔係咁做。。<br />\n<br />\n美甲師，希望你好好反省下，你每搽一隻指甲都出界，基本功都未做好，甲型都整唔好，你好好諗下自己係咪應該繼續呢條路。係既話，請你用心學習路好再走堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老闆們，希望你地好好諗下係咪仲係請學徒做，咁樣真係好倒米。。。<br />\n<br />\n我已經約好聽日去拆左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識我既都應該已經知我有幾嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d21fe8330944acc9e5113d0b53b13cfcd16ef7","tid":1941711,"uid":3820,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T14:56:57.000Z","msg":"手指好長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748afbc4231510b098a762c2b8b2f27bab9816ee","tid":1941711,"uid":246305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T15:13:01.000Z","msg":"好唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有坑既"},{"pid":"2152501362635e489fa77904868b4cb4cdee2468","tid":1941711,"uid":317376,"like":46,"dislike":3,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T15:14:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但你搭地鐵</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下次唔好啦&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be8f4b7f3797015aeb961c7658ff8448593c18a","tid":1941711,"uid":254302,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2152501362635e489fa77904868b4cb4cdee2468","tid":1941711,"uid":317376,"like":46,"dislike":3,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T15:14:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但你搭地鐵</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下次唔好啦&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T15:23:48.000Z","msg":"幫你好好咁教訓佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa4caa384783aa2872e8d0c9b0e5eed40c3a6ff","tid":1941711,"uid":254302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T15:24:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bb400e1911564f0c2b935226ea55c8ad372e1a8","tid":1941711,"uid":160348,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T15:24:33.0